WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.909 --> 00:00:08.910
In the Western countries, there is this two-party
game. There is this Liberal, and the Conservative.

00:00:08.910 --> 00:00:15.400
They would use terms like Democrats and Republicans.
One is modern and progressive, and the other

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:24.070
is traditional and conservative. In fact,
Churchill made this very interesting observation.

00:00:24.070 --> 00:00:32.360
He said, "If you are not a liberal at twenty,
you have no heart. And, if you're not a conservative,

00:00:32.360 --> 00:00:41.250
when you grow older, forty, you have no brain"!
Which is the right attitude to have? Should

00:00:41.250 --> 00:00:51.090
we have both??
